1
00:02:11,500 --> 00:02:13,416
[NARRATOR]
Last time on Dragon Ball,

2
00:02:13,500 --> 00:02:15,708
the countdown to victory began

3
00:02:15,791 --> 00:02:19,250
with Goku poised to win the
World Martial Arts Tournament.

4
00:02:19,333 --> 00:02:22,500
However, Junior put
a hole in Goku's plan

5
00:02:22,583 --> 00:02:24,791
by bouncing back
with a surprise attack

6
00:02:24,875 --> 00:02:26,750
that nearly destroyed
the young hero.

7
00:02:26,833 --> 00:02:28,500
[CHICHI]
You monster!

8
00:02:28,583 --> 00:02:31,208
[NARRATOR] As Junior
prepared to stamp Goku out,

9
00:02:31,291 --> 00:02:33,541
his friends came to the rescue.

10
00:02:33,625 --> 00:02:37,458
Unfortunately, they failed.
But, they were able to distract

11
00:02:37,541 --> 00:02:40,916
the sinister warrior long
enough for Goku to recover.

12
00:02:41,000 --> 00:02:43,375
[GOKU] Good thing you aim
as bad as you fight!

13
00:02:43,458 --> 00:02:45,250
You missed my vital organs.

14
00:02:45,333 --> 00:02:47,833
All of them?

15
00:02:47,916 --> 00:02:50,208
[NARRATOR] Junior was shocked
by Goku's declaration

16
00:02:50,291 --> 00:02:51,958
to continue the match.

17
00:02:52,041 --> 00:02:53,583
It was clear to both opponents

18
00:02:53,666 --> 00:02:57,583
that this fight had become
a matter of life or death.

19
00:02:57,666 --> 00:03:00,250
And now, the final confrontation

20
00:03:00,333 --> 00:03:04,833
to determine the real
master of martial arts!

21
00:03:21,541 --> 00:03:22,791
[growling]

22
