[GOKU screams]

27
00:03:32,458 --> 00:03:34,125
[ALL shriek]

28
00:03:34,208 --> 00:03:35,708
[GOKU groans]

29
00:03:35,791 --> 00:03:40,791
[panting]

30
00:03:42,166 --> 00:03:52,000
[groaning]

