41
00:04:27,166 --> 00:04:28,458
[PICCOLO JR.]
After all the hard work

42
00:04:28,541 --> 00:04:30,250
I put into renovating
this place,

43
00:04:30,333 --> 00:04:33,250
the least you could do is
stop leaking on the floor.

44
00:04:33,333 --> 00:04:37,666
[groans, pants]

45
00:04:37,750 --> 00:04:39,833
Watch out, Goku!

46
00:04:39,916 --> 00:04:40,416
Uhh?

47
00:04:40,500 --> 00:04:45,416
[roaring]

48
00:04:45,500 --> 00:04:47,375
[screams]

49
00:04:47,458 --> 00:04:48,833
[PICCOLO JR. roars]

50
00:04:48,916 --> 00:04:50,750
[GOKU shrieks]

51
00:04:50,833 --> 00:04:55,083
--[GOKU screams]
--[PICCOLO JR. laughs]

52
00:04:55,166 --> 00:04:57,250
[GOKU groans]

53
00:04:57,333 --> 00:05:00,916
[PICCOLO JR. roars]

54
00:05:01,000 --> 00:05:02,333
[GOKU gasps]

55
00:05:02,416 --> 00:05:05,666
--[GOKU shrieks]
--[PICCOLO JR. roars]

56
00:05:05,750 --> 00:05:07,625
[screaming]

57
00:05:07,708 --> 00:05:09,375
