58
00:05:09,458 --> 00:05:13,375
--[GOKU sputters]
--[PICCOLO JR. laughs]

59
00:05:13,458 --> 00:05:15,833
That's it. I can't
watch any more of this!

60
00:05:15,916 --> 00:05:18,666
--[GOKU groans]
--[PICCOLO JR. laughs]

61
00:05:18,750 --> 00:05:21,083
[PICCOLO JR.]
I'd just like to thank you.

62
00:05:21,166 --> 00:05:23,541
Seeing you lying in
the dirt, writhing in pain

63
00:05:23,625 --> 00:05:26,583
means more to me than you
could possibly imagine.

64
00:05:26,666 --> 00:05:28,833
[GOKU sputters]

65
00:05:28,916 --> 00:05:31,291
[laughing]

66
00:05:31,375 --> 00:05:32,791
[GOKU screams]

67
00:05:32,875 --> 00:05:34,333
[PICCOLO JR.] My father lost
much during his last battle,

68
00:05:34,416 --> 00:05:36,083
including his left arm.

69
00:05:36,166 --> 00:05:39,125
Goku!

70
00:05:39,208 --> 00:05:42,208
[KAMI gasps]

71
00:05:42,291 --> 00:05:47,166
Allow me to extend you the
same courtesy you gave him.

72
00:05:47,250 --> 00:05:48,416
[BOTH whimper]

73
00:05:48,500 --> 00:05:49,416
Oh, no!

74
00:05:49,500 --> 00:05:55,375
[GOKU whimpers]

75
00:05:55,458 --> 00:05:57,333
[PICCOLO JR.] All right.
I won't take your arm,

76
00:05:57,416 --> 00:05:59,625
but you get the idea.

77
00:05:59,708 --> 00:06:03,041
I've deprived you of
the use of your body.

78
00:06:03,125 --> 00:06:06,583
[GOKU groans]

79
00:06:06,666 --> 00:06:10,791
And now, Goku, I will
deprive you of your life.

80
00:06:15,083 --> 00:06:17,291
[GOKU groans]

81
00:06:20,583 --> 00:06:22,750
--[OOLANG whimpers]
--[PUAR shrieks]

82
00:06:22,833 --> 00:06:24,250
[BOTH whimper]

83
00:06:24,333 --> 00:06:27,041
H-He's going to kill Goku!

84
00:06:27,125 --> 00:06:28,625
He doesn't care
about the tournament.

85
00:06:28,708 --> 00:06:30,291
He just wants to win!

86
00:06:30,375 --> 00:06:31,666
Didn't you hear what I said!

87
00:06:31,750 --> 00:06:33,541
We can't just stand by
and let this happen.

88
00:06:33,625 --> 00:06:39,291
[GOKU groans]

89
00:06:41,625 --> 00:06:46,000
[ALL whimpering]

90
00:06:50,833 --> 00:06:54,291
This has gone far
enough! Please stop!

91
00:06:57,000 --> 00:06:58,500
Tien Shinhan, isn't it?

92
00:06:58,583 --> 00:07:00,208
Uh?

93
00:07:00,291 --> 00:07:03,416
You can save Goku
if you kill me.

94
00:07:03,500 --> 00:07:04,875
What?

95
00:07:04,958 --> 00:07:06,875
Junior will die, too.

96
00:07:06,958 --> 00:07:09,041
--We can't hurt you, Kami.
--Yeah!

97
00:07:09,125 --> 00:07:12,166
What are you waitin' for?
He's right, kill him!

98
00:07:12,250 --> 00:07:13,333
Uhh...

99
00:07:13,416 --> 00:07:16,458
You must hurry...
before it's too late.

100
00:07:16,541 --> 00:07:19,125
[TIEN grunts]

101
00:07:19,208 --> 00:07:21,666
Tien, I cannot destroy myself.

102
00:07:21,750 --> 00:07:25,333
If you want to save him,
this may be your only chance.

103
00:07:25,416 --> 00:07:27,750
But... I can't!

104
00:07:27,833 --> 00:07:31,500
My demise does not
have to be permanent.

105
00:07:31,583 --> 00:07:33,125
Once Junior is destroyed,

106
00:07:33,208 --> 00:07:36,708
you can ask for the Eternal
Dragon to resuscitate me.

107
00:07:36,791 --> 00:07:38,541
There's no time to waste.

108
00:07:38,625 --> 00:07:40,083
[TIEN grunts]

109
00:07:44,750 --> 00:07:47,000
[PICCOLO JR. growls]

110
00:07:48,625 --> 00:07:50,500
[KAMI]
Tien Shinhan?

111
00:07:50,583 --> 00:07:51,750
[grunts]

112
00:07:51,833 --> 00:07:53,916
Okay, I will do it.

113
00:07:54,000 --> 00:07:55,250
[BOTH gasp]

114
00:07:55,333 --> 00:07:59,291
[KAMI]
Hmm... Hmmm...

115
00:07:59,375 --> 00:08:01,000
[TIEN grunts]

116
00:08:09,250 --> 00:08:10,041
[TIEN grunts]

117
00:08:10,125 --> 00:08:11,458
[GOKU]
Don't do it!

118
00:08:11,541 --> 00:08:12,166
Uh?

119
00:08:12,250 --> 00:08:13,458
[KAMI]
Huh?

120
00:08:13,541 --> 00:08:17,375
[GOKU]
That's... It's not necessary!

121
00:08:17,458 --> 00:08:18,916
[TIEN gasps]

122
00:08:19,000 --> 00:08:20,333
[KAMI gasps]

123
00:08:20,416 --> 00:08:23,666
[GOKU groans]

124
00:08:23,750 --> 00:08:26,625
I know I can win!

125
00:08:26,708 --> 00:08:28,708
Are you sure you can beat him?

126
00:08:28,791 --> 00:08:32,125
No! You can't even move.
That's just impossible!

127
00:08:32,208 --> 00:08:35,916
He is right, Goku!
You don't have a chance!

128
00:08:36,000 --> 00:08:37,166
[TIEN grunts]

129
00:08:37,250 --> 00:08:40,791
[PICCOLO JR. laughs]

130
00:08:40,875 --> 00:08:43,500
[PICCOLO JR. roars]

131
00:08:43,583 --> 00:08:45,375
[GOKU whimpers]

132
00:08:45,458 --> 00:08:51,083
[roaring continues]

133
00:08:51,166 --> 00:08:52,333
Too late!

134
00:08:52,416 --> 00:08:54,166
[roaring continues]

135
00:08:54,250 --> 00:08:55,250
[BOTH scream]

136
00:08:55,333 --> 00:08:57,375
[GOKU groans]

137
00:08:57,458 --> 00:08:59,750
--[GOKU whimpers]
--[PICCOLO JR. roars]

138
00:08:59,833 --> 00:09:00,541
[GOKU yelps]

139
00:09:00,625 --> 00:09:04,041
[PICCOLO JR. roars]

140
00:09:04,125 --> 00:09:06,166
[KRILLIN, TIEN yell]

141
00:09:07,083 --> 00:09:11,000
Relax and enjoy your death.
You have nowhere else to go!

142
00:09:11,083 --> 00:09:15,125
[PICCOLO JR. laughs]

143
00:09:15,208 --> 00:09:16,291
[PUAR, OOLANG scream]

144
00:09:16,375 --> 00:09:18,125
[LAUNCH, BULMA scream]

145
00:09:18,208 --> 00:09:18,875
[CHICHI]
No!

146
00:09:18,958 --> 00:09:20,416
[GOKU whimpers]

147
00:09:20,500 --> 00:09:25,666
[GOKU yelps, whimpers]

148
00:09:25,750 --> 00:09:29,958
[CHICHI yells]

149
00:09:33,333 --> 00:09:38,666
[ALL groaning, yelping]

150
00:09:38,750 --> 00:09:40,791
[KRILLIN yells]

151
00:09:43,291 --> 00:09:45,291
[BOTH scream]

152
00:09:47,291 --> 00:09:48,750
--[YAMCHA grunts]
--[CHICHI screams]

153
00:09:48,833 --> 00:09:51,458
[PICCOLO JR. laughs]

154
00:09:51,541 --> 00:09:53,500
[PICCOLO JR. pants]

155
00:09:53,583 --> 00:09:55,458
[BOTH groan]

156
00:09:58,083 --> 00:10:01,000
--[LAUNCH groans]
--[BULMA groans, yelps]

157
00:10:01,083 --> 00:10:05,833
[PICCOLO JR. pants]

158
00:10:05,916 --> 00:10:11,666
[PICCOLO JR. laughs]

159
00:10:11,750 --> 00:10:13,458
[KAMI whimpers]

160
00:10:13,541 --> 00:10:16,583
[KAMI gasps]

161
00:10:16,666 --> 00:10:22,708
[ALL groan]

162
00:10:22,791 --> 00:10:29,375
[PICCOLO JR. laughs]

163
00:10:37,375 --> 00:10:39,250
[PICCOLO JR. laughs]

164
00:10:39,333 --> 00:10:43,791
[PICCOLO JR.] It's done! It's
too bad you were obliterated.

165
00:10:43,875 --> 00:10:46,666
I would like to have kept
some of you as a souvenir!

166
00:10:46,750 --> 00:10:48,708
[PICCOLO JR. laughs]

167
00:10:48,791 --> 00:10:50,625
[CHICHI]
Uhh... Is he--

168
00:10:50,708 --> 00:10:57,208
[PICCOLO JR. laughs]

169
00:10:57,291 --> 00:11:00,500
I've won! Goku is no more!

170
00:11:00,583 --> 00:11:05,333
The world is now mine
to do with what I will!

171
00:11:05,416 --> 00:11:09,791
A new age will soon
dawn on the Earth!

172
00:11:09,875 --> 00:11:14,333
One marked by suffering, pain,
and torment for all humankind!

173
00:11:14,416 --> 00:11:19,541
Goku! I never thought I'd be
a widow before I was a bride!

174
00:11:19,625 --> 00:11:24,291
[CHICHI cries]

175
00:11:24,375 --> 00:11:27,208
--[OOLANG grunts]
--[PUAR coughs, yelps]

176
00:11:27,291 --> 00:11:29,666
You're gonna pay for this!

177
00:11:29,750 --> 00:11:32,583
It's a pity. Goku deserved
better than this.

178
00:11:32,666 --> 00:11:34,000
Ohh...

179
00:11:34,083 --> 00:11:35,541
[PICCOLO JR. laughs]

180
00:11:35,625 --> 00:11:38,458
There's no need to grieve
for your fallen companion.

181
00:11:38,541 --> 00:11:40,583
You'll be joining him shortly.

182
00:11:40,666 --> 00:11:41,833
[BOTH scream]

183
00:11:41,916 --> 00:11:43,291
--[KRILLIN grunts]
--Monster!

184
00:11:43,375 --> 00:11:46,708
You can all keep Goku
company in the afterlife.

185
00:11:46,791 --> 00:11:50,250
[TIEN, KRILLIN, YAMCHA grunt]

186
00:11:51,791 --> 00:11:59,666
[PICCOLO JR. laughs]

187
00:11:59,750 --> 00:12:01,625
[KRILLIN pants]

188
00:12:01,708 --> 00:12:02,833
Ah?

189
00:12:04,291 --> 00:12:07,625
[whimpers]

190
00:12:07,708 --> 00:12:08,875
What's the matter?

191
00:12:08,958 --> 00:12:11,166
[KRILLIN]
Up above! Isn't that--?

192
00:12:11,250 --> 00:12:12,458
[TIEN grunts]

193
00:12:12,541 --> 00:12:16,833
[PICCOLO JR. laughs]

194
00:12:16,916 --> 00:12:20,000
--[KAMI] Uhh.. Ah...
--[ROSHI gasps, laughs]

195
00:12:20,083 --> 00:12:21,708
Goku!

196
00:12:21,791 --> 00:12:23,250
[PICCOLO JR.]
Huh?

197
00:12:23,333 --> 00:12:26,416
Well, look who's coming back!

198
00:12:29,250 --> 00:12:30,208
[yelps]

199
00:12:42,416 --> 00:12:43,791
[ROSHI]
Ehh...

200
00:12:43,875 --> 00:12:45,250
[yelps]

201
00:12:46,875 --> 00:12:48,541
[BOTH]
Do it, Goku!

202
00:12:49,833 --> 00:12:51,833
[GOKU]
I told you I'd win!

203
00:12:51,916 --> 00:12:53,041
[PICCOLO JR. screams]

204
00:12:53,125 --> 00:12:57,250
--[GOKU yells]
--[PICCOLO JR. screams]

205
00:12:57,333 --> 00:13:03,250
[PICCOLO JR. groans]

206
00:13:04,250 --> 00:13:06,458
[PICCOLO JR. grunts]

207
00:13:06,541 --> 00:13:08,375
[GOKU grunts]

208
00:13:08,458 --> 00:13:10,333
[PICCOLO JR.]
Uh...

209
00:13:14,250 --> 00:13:18,250
--[PICCOLO JR. groans]
--[ANNOUNCER whimpers]

210
00:13:18,333 --> 00:13:19,666
[GOKU]
Was it far enough?

211
00:13:19,750 --> 00:13:20,625
Huh?

212
00:13:20,708 --> 00:13:26,166
Is he outside-ohh...
the ring?

213
00:13:26,250 --> 00:13:31,625
[ANNOUNCER whimpers]

214
00:13:31,708 --> 00:13:33,416
[ANNOUNCER]
There's not much left.

215
00:13:33,500 --> 00:13:37,750
[GOKU]
Can you tell? Have I won?

216
00:13:37,833 --> 00:13:41,208
[ANNOUNCER whimpers]

217
00:13:41,291 --> 00:13:46,625
Well... uh, it appears
Junior is out of bounds.

218
00:13:46,708 --> 00:13:51,333
The winner of the 23rd World
Martial Arts Tournament is Goku!

219
00:13:51,416 --> 00:13:54,583
[GOKU laughs]

220
00:13:54,666 --> 00:13:56,583
--[KRILLIN] All right!
--[ROSHI] Fantastic!

221
00:13:56,666 --> 00:13:58,583
[BOTH laugh]

222
00:13:58,666 --> 00:14:03,416
[LAUNCH, PUAR, CHICHI, YAMCHA,
KRILLIN] Yeah! You did it! Yeah!

223
00:14:04,958 --> 00:14:06,666
[YAJIROBE grunts]

224
00:14:06,750 --> 00:14:11,125
It's about time! Is it
safe to come out now?

225
00:14:11,208 --> 00:14:14,583
Good work! Boy,
you look terrible.

226
00:14:14,666 --> 00:14:17,208
You're safe now.
How do you feel?

227
00:14:17,291 --> 00:14:19,583
My body's numb and
my head's pounding.

228
00:14:19,666 --> 00:14:22,791
But, other than that,
I feel great.

229
00:14:22,875 --> 00:14:24,375
[YAJIROBE groans]

230
00:14:24,458 --> 00:14:27,958
[ROSHI] Funny, they never look
psychotic when they're sleeping.

231
00:14:29,500 --> 00:14:31,666
[KAMI]
Hmm...

232
00:14:31,750 --> 00:14:33,208
[YAJIROBE]
Do you have plans for Junior?

233
00:14:33,291 --> 00:14:34,125
[BULMA, CHICHI,
YAMCHA, KRILLIN gasp]

234
00:14:34,208 --> 00:14:35,291
[YAJIROBE]
I'm hungry.

235
00:14:35,375 --> 00:14:38,375
Yajirobe! What about your beans?

236
00:14:38,458 --> 00:14:42,208
I want some real food.
You want beans? Here.

237
00:14:42,291 --> 00:14:44,208
Have a bean buffet.

238
00:14:44,291 --> 00:14:46,583
Ah, thank you! Ahh.

239
00:14:46,666 --> 00:14:48,750
[GOKU chews]

240
00:14:48,833 --> 00:14:50,875
[ALL gasp, whimper]

241
00:14:50,958 --> 00:14:54,833
[GOKU chews]

242
00:14:54,916 --> 00:14:56,333
[GOKU groans]

243
00:14:56,416 --> 00:14:58,166
[YAJIROBE grunts]

244
00:14:58,250 --> 00:15:00,833
--[GOKU laughs]
--[CHICHI giggles]

245
00:15:00,916 --> 00:15:05,500
[GOKU grunts]

246
00:15:05,583 --> 00:15:06,541
Ah. Hah.

247
00:15:06,625 --> 00:15:07,708
[ALL gasp]

248
00:15:07,791 --> 00:15:09,875
[GOKU]
Woohoo! I did it! I've won!

249
00:15:09,958 --> 00:15:15,458
Yes! I'm the champion!
Yeah-ha-ha! Woohoo! Yeah!

250
00:15:15,541 --> 00:15:18,500
Ha-ha. He-he. I won! I won!

251
00:15:18,583 --> 00:15:22,166
[CHICHI] I've never
seen him so happy!

252
00:15:22,250 --> 00:15:25,708
I didn't know those beans could
heal you as well as fill you up.

253
00:15:25,791 --> 00:15:27,416
Yeah well, I still
can't understand

254
00:15:27,500 --> 00:15:29,666
why they taste like fish.

255
00:15:29,750 --> 00:15:31,125
[GOKU]
I won! Yeah-ha!

256
00:15:31,208 --> 00:15:33,958
Amazing.

257
00:15:34,041 --> 00:15:37,541
[KAMI]
Mhm... hmm...

258
00:15:37,625 --> 00:15:39,416
Yeah!

259
00:15:39,500 --> 00:15:40,541
Uh? Huh?

260
00:15:40,625 --> 00:15:42,458
[KAMI groans]

261
00:15:42,541 --> 00:15:43,958
Ah...

262
00:15:44,041 --> 00:15:46,000
No, Kami!

263
00:15:46,083 --> 00:15:47,291
[KAMI]
No more.

264
00:15:47,375 --> 00:15:49,333
[KAMI grunts]

265
00:15:49,416 --> 00:15:52,333
[PICCOLO JR. groans]

266
00:15:52,416 --> 00:15:54,833
No!

267
00:15:54,916 --> 00:15:56,666
[KAMI]
Huh?

268
00:15:56,750 --> 00:15:57,916
Get out of my way!

269
00:15:58,000 --> 00:16:01,250
No, first tell me what
you're planning to do.

270
00:16:03,541 --> 00:16:05,125
[KAMI grunts]

271
00:16:08,916 --> 00:16:11,416
[KAMI]
He is still alive!

272
00:16:11,500 --> 00:16:13,875
You know the danger he poses.

273
00:16:13,958 --> 00:16:17,541
This world will never be safe
until he stops breathing.

274
00:16:17,625 --> 00:16:19,625
[PICCOLO JR. groans]

275
00:16:19,708 --> 00:16:22,250
Pure evil can never be tamed.

276
00:16:22,333 --> 00:16:24,958
But if he dies,
you'll go with him.

277
00:16:25,041 --> 00:16:27,916
There has to be another
option besides destroying him.

278
00:16:28,000 --> 00:16:31,500
I've already explained to you
that destroying me won't matter.

279
00:16:31,583 --> 00:16:35,500
You can ask the Eternal Dragon
to bring me back again.

280
00:16:35,583 --> 00:16:37,541
Kami is right, Goku.

281
00:16:37,625 --> 00:16:41,166
Trust him. His plan will work.

282
00:16:41,250 --> 00:16:44,375
But you're Kami. Are you
capable of telling a lie?

283
00:16:44,458 --> 00:16:45,875
Say what?

284
00:16:45,958 --> 00:16:48,125
The Eternal Dragon
and Dragon Balls

285
00:16:48,208 --> 00:16:50,750
were created by Kami, right?

286
00:16:50,833 --> 00:16:53,375
[KAMI grunts]

287
00:16:53,458 --> 00:16:56,750
So, then it's safe to assume
that if Kami is destroyed,

288
00:16:56,833 --> 00:17:00,375
the Dragon Balls will
disappear as well, correct?

289
00:17:00,458 --> 00:17:01,875
[KAMI]
Ohh...

290
00:17:01,958 --> 00:17:03,041
What's that?

291
00:17:03,125 --> 00:17:04,833
[ROSHI]
Ehh...

292
00:17:10,875 --> 00:17:12,583
[KAMI]
Hmm.

293
00:17:16,875 --> 00:17:19,250
Hmm...

294
00:17:24,541 --> 00:17:28,708
Sometimes, even I
will make a mistake.

295
00:17:32,416 --> 00:17:33,875
I created this monster.

296
00:17:33,958 --> 00:17:37,000
Yet, he's become so powerful
as to surpass even me,

297
00:17:37,083 --> 00:17:39,750
plunging the world into chaos!

298
00:17:43,750 --> 00:17:46,875
I've lost more than power.
I've lost my perspective.

299
00:17:46,958 --> 00:17:50,958
I no longer deserve to
govern this or any world.

300
00:17:51,041 --> 00:17:53,416
How can you say such
things, when it was you

301
00:17:53,500 --> 00:17:56,000
who brought our
world peace again?

302
00:17:56,083 --> 00:17:57,583
If not for your training,

303
00:17:57,666 --> 00:18:00,750
Goku would never have attained
the level of skill he has now.

304
00:18:00,833 --> 00:18:02,041
Junior would have won.

305
00:18:02,125 --> 00:18:04,333
And if the Dragon Balls
hadn't been forged,

306
00:18:04,416 --> 00:18:07,250
none of these young warriors
would have ever met.

307
00:18:07,333 --> 00:18:09,708
And I can't begin to count
the number of people

308
00:18:09,791 --> 00:18:12,833
who owe their lives
to these kids.

309
00:18:14,291 --> 00:18:17,416
When their quest began,
they were just children.

310
00:18:17,500 --> 00:18:20,041
But they soon grew into heroes.

311
00:18:21,875 --> 00:18:23,750
Yeah!

312
00:18:23,833 --> 00:18:28,541
When the world needed saving,
eight kids answered the call.

313
00:18:32,958 --> 00:18:36,875
One ball, that's
how it all began.

314
00:18:42,208 --> 00:18:47,375
Goku, you're fortunate to have
had such an excellent teacher.

315
00:18:47,458 --> 00:18:48,625
[GOKU]
Mh-hm.

316
00:18:48,708 --> 00:18:50,791
No one is more wise or as goofy.

317
00:18:50,875 --> 00:18:52,208
--[ROSHI] Mhm?
--[TIEN laughs]

318
00:18:52,291 --> 00:18:55,458
No, no. Really, I just
taught him a few basic skills.

319
00:18:55,541 --> 00:18:57,666
I couldn't have raised them
into such fine warriors

320
00:18:57,750 --> 00:19:00,875
without the aid of you
and Master Korin. Heh...

321
00:19:00,958 --> 00:19:04,916
[BOTH laugh, gasp]

322
00:19:05,000 --> 00:19:07,458
[GOKU]
Uhh...

323
00:19:07,541 --> 00:19:09,916
--[KAMI grunts]
--[GOKU yelps]

324
00:19:10,000 --> 00:19:13,541
[GOKU grunts]

325
00:19:13,625 --> 00:19:15,875
[GOKU laughs]

326
00:19:15,958 --> 00:19:17,875
Wear the symbol of
the turtle with pride.

327
00:19:17,958 --> 00:19:20,333
Never forget where
you came from.

328
00:19:21,666 --> 00:19:23,750
[GOKU]
Thank you.

329
00:19:23,833 --> 00:19:26,916
Yajirobe, can I have
another Senzu bean?

330
00:19:27,000 --> 00:19:28,833
[YAJIROBE grunts]

331
00:19:28,916 --> 00:19:32,333
If you keep eating like this,
you're gonna get fat! Here!

332
00:19:32,416 --> 00:19:33,250
Thanks.

333
00:19:33,333 --> 00:19:34,958
[PICCOLO JR. groans]

334
00:19:35,041 --> 00:19:36,000
Eat up.

335
00:19:36,083 --> 00:19:37,333
--[ROSHI] No! Don't.
--[KAMI] Goku!

336
00:19:37,416 --> 00:19:38,666
[KAMI]
What're you doing?

337
00:19:38,750 --> 00:19:41,791
Stop! Are you crazy?
We don't wanna wake him up!

338
00:19:41,875 --> 00:19:46,875
[PICCOLO JR. groans]

339
00:19:46,958 --> 00:19:48,333
Ah! Ah... Ah.

340
00:19:48,416 --> 00:19:54,583
[PICCOLO JR. grunts]

341
00:19:54,666 --> 00:20:00,333
[PICCOLO JR. laughs]

342
00:20:00,416 --> 00:20:03,166
[ALL yelp]

343
00:20:03,250 --> 00:20:06,208
That's just great! Maybe you
two can become best friends!

344
00:20:06,291 --> 00:20:07,500
Goku!

345
00:20:07,583 --> 00:20:09,375
[GOKU] My reason for
helping you is simple.

346
00:20:09,458 --> 00:20:13,000
If I destroyed you,
Kami would suffer as well.

347
00:20:14,791 --> 00:20:16,416
Besides, without a
rival to fight,

348
00:20:16,500 --> 00:20:20,000
I wouldn't have much to do. You
seem to fit that role nicely.

349
00:20:20,083 --> 00:20:22,208
[PICCOLO JR. laughs]

350
00:20:22,291 --> 00:20:24,625
You're a moron if you
think this changes

351
00:20:24,708 --> 00:20:27,208
anything between you and I.

352
00:20:27,291 --> 00:20:29,291
Mercy is a loathsome trait,

353
00:20:29,375 --> 00:20:32,916
and you will soon learn
that I have no such weakness.

354
00:20:33,000 --> 00:20:36,583
When that glorious day arrives,
the whole world will be mine!

355
00:20:36,666 --> 00:20:38,541
[ROSHI thinking]
He will never stop.

356
00:20:38,625 --> 00:20:40,958
[PICCOLO JR. laughs]

357
00:20:41,041 --> 00:20:44,416
Let's just hope between now
and then he discovers a hobby!

358
00:20:44,500 --> 00:20:45,958
[PICCOLO JR.]
I'll see you real soon.

359
00:20:46,041 --> 00:20:48,791
Until then, I'll see you
in your nightmares!

360
00:20:49,916 --> 00:20:51,208
[GOKU thinking]
When that day comes,

361
00:20:51,291 --> 00:20:53,000
I hope you're not
too disappointed.

362
00:20:53,083 --> 00:20:56,416
I've beaten you once.
And I'll do it again.

363
00:20:59,041 --> 00:21:00,458
[BULMA thinking]
It's difficult to believe

364
00:21:00,541 --> 00:21:02,791
that little boy I found in
the woods all those years ago

365
00:21:02,875 --> 00:21:04,833
is now a martial arts champion.

366
00:21:04,916 --> 00:21:08,416
I can't wait to see
what he does next.

367
00:21:08,500 --> 00:21:10,416
[CHICHI]
Goku! You did it!

368
00:21:10,500 --> 00:21:13,083
You did it! You're so brave!

369
00:21:13,166 --> 00:21:14,333
--[GOKU gasps]
--[CHICHI] And you're alive!

370
00:21:14,416 --> 00:21:17,166
I'm so proud of you! Oh...

371
00:21:17,250 --> 00:21:20,500
Easy, easy! ChiChi, please,
not in front of everyone!

372
00:21:20,583 --> 00:21:22,625
He-he. You've just
discovered the one thing

373
00:21:22,708 --> 00:21:26,750
you'll never be able to
defeat. Love conquers all.

374
00:21:26,833 --> 00:21:30,500
Good work. Oh, and, Tien,
are you expecting a visitor?

375
00:21:30,583 --> 00:21:32,000
What? Hey!

376
00:21:32,083 --> 00:21:33,458
[ALL]
Uh?

377
00:21:33,541 --> 00:21:35,000
[CHIAOTZU]
Tien!

378
00:21:35,083 --> 00:21:36,125
[CHIAOTZU laughs]

379
00:21:36,208 --> 00:21:37,916
[TIEN]
Chiaotzu! You're alive!

380
00:21:38,000 --> 00:21:39,208
--[GOKU chuckles]
--[KAMI] Goku.

381
00:21:39,291 --> 00:21:40,541
[GOKU]
Uh?

382
00:21:40,625 --> 00:21:42,375
You've proven yourself
worthy. In fact, I'd like

383
00:21:42,458 --> 00:21:44,291
to offer you my job.

384
00:21:44,375 --> 00:21:47,041
Uh? Me? Are you serious?

385
00:21:47,125 --> 00:21:50,333
Mh-hm. I have the utmost
confidence in you.

386
00:21:50,416 --> 00:21:53,083
It could be your
greatest adventure.

387
00:21:53,166 --> 00:21:54,833
No, no, no, no, no! I couldn't.

388
00:21:54,916 --> 00:21:56,583
I appreciate your
confidence in my abilities,

389
00:21:56,666 --> 00:21:58,416
but that's not the
adventure I'm looking for.

390
00:21:58,500 --> 00:21:59,791
It's your job, keep it!

391
00:21:59,875 --> 00:22:01,208
Don't be hasty.

392
00:22:01,291 --> 00:22:04,625
Think of all the good you
could do with that power!

393
00:22:04,708 --> 00:22:07,208
You are the only one I
could trust to succeed me.

394
00:22:07,291 --> 00:22:08,916
What do you say?

395
00:22:09,000 --> 00:22:10,000
[GOKU laughs]

396
00:22:10,083 --> 00:22:11,250
[KAMI gasps]

397
00:22:12,125 --> 00:22:14,208
[GOKU]
Flying Nimbus!

398
00:22:16,833 --> 00:22:20,958
--[GOKU] Heh. Let's go!
--[CHICHI giggles]

399
00:22:21,041 --> 00:22:26,166
Sorry, Kami! But it doesn't
get any better than this!

400
00:22:26,250 --> 00:22:28,500
[ALL]
Goodbye, Goku!

401
00:22:28,583 --> 00:22:30,750
[KRILLIN, ROSHI laugh]

402
00:22:30,833 --> 00:22:34,041
[CHICHI laughs]

403
00:22:35,333 --> 00:22:39,375
Hmm... I guess this is the end.

404
00:22:39,458 --> 00:22:40,541
[ROSHI yelps]

405
00:22:40,625 --> 00:22:43,250
[ROSHI]
Oh-ho... That... stings.

406
00:22:43,333 --> 00:22:44,416
[NARRATOR]
No one can say

407
00:22:44,500 --> 00:22:47,083
what tomorrow will
bring for our heroes.

408
00:22:47,166 --> 00:22:51,333
But one thing is certain,
wherever adventure exists,

409
00:22:51,416 --> 00:22:55,416
Goku will be there!

